As we provided an update on our strategic plan really in January of this year, I think the market context of that time is also of note. First, really, we saw a challenging interest rate outlook ahead of us and more importantly, we saw a lot of excess capital in the commercial insurance space. So our plan really focussed on aligning three things; revenues where we were targeting shrinking, expenses where we were accelerating our expense reduction plan and finally capital where we were committed to returning excess capital to shareholders.
