I\xe2\x80\x99m going to turn the page -- as we\xe2\x80\x99ve said before we really feel AIG is best valued and best in three parts. First, in blue the operating portfolio, this is about three quarters of the company\xe2\x80\x99s capital and is our core business. If you were targeting at 10% return on equity and growth in strategic segments.
